The paper deals with summarizing and querying labeled-graph streams, which involves processing large volumes of data in real-time. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of databases (cs.DB), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), or social and information networks (cs.SI). However, since the paper focuses on graph streams and their summarization, it is most likely to belong to cs.DB or cs.DS.
